
{
  "$schema": "https://app-schema.heroku.com/Schema",
  "name": "Telegram Chat Bot - Mere Harry",
  "description": "AI Powered Telegram Chat Bot in Python",
  "buildpacks": [
    {
      "url": "heroku/python"
    }
  ],
  "stack": "heroku-22",
  "env": {
    "TOKEN": {"required": true, "description": "Telegram Bot Token"},
    "PYTHON_VERSION": "3.11.0",
    "NLTK_DATA": {"value": "/app/nltk_data"}
  }
}
```
Lekin mere Harry, yeh file mein `TOKEN` ko environment variable ke roop mein set karna hai Heroku dashboard par ya Heroku CLI se. 
**Heroku CLI command:**
```
heroku config:set TOKEN=YOUR_TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN
```
Replace `YOUR_TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN` with actual token!
